==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unshale
<hw>Un*shale"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>shale</ets>.]</ety> <def>To strip the shale, or
husk, from; to uncover.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I will not <qex>unshale</qex> the jest before it be ripe.</q>
<rj><qau>Marston.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unshape</ent>⟦br⟧
